'''Atlantica-Séguier''' (Created in 1984) is a French [[publishing house]].
==Background== Created in 1984, the company has published more than 2,300 works which include [[fiction]] and [[non-fiction]] books as well as plays. The non-fiction focus is mainly on cinema, the theater, and painting as well as some specialty sports such as bullfighting. The company is headquartered in [[Biarritz|Biarritz, France]] and [[Paris|Paris, France]]. <ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.atlantica.fr/atlantica.php? |title=Atlantica France|date=accessed 24 January 2010 |language=French}}</ref>
==Works== Works published by Atlantica-Séguier include: *''[[Gabriel Dupont]] (1878–1914) ou La Mélancolie du Bonheur'', by Philippe Simon *''Gibraltar, roisée de mondes et Gibraltar, improbable frontière'' by [[Zakya Daoud]] *''Les Cadavres Hilares'', by [[Lily Bloom]] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theatreonline.com/guide/detail_artiste.asp?i_Artiste=43441&i_Qualite=1|title=Theatre Online |date=accessed 24 January 2010 }}</ref> * ''[[Maurice Duruflé]] : Souvenirs et autres écrits'', by Frédéric Blan ISBN 2-84049-411-6
