The art of '''book rebinding''' involves a used or treasured [[book]] and rebinding it to protect it, or continue the life of the book. Popular rebinding materials include [[leather]]. The process usually includes reinforcement of the book signatures and then a recovering process begins. The most popular books to be rebound is the [[Bible]]. 

