'''Comics''' are an art form using a single image or a series of static images in fixed sequence. [[Cartoons]] and [[comic strips]] are often printed in [[newspaper]]s, while [[comic book]]s are generally published as individual documents. [[Webcomic]]s are published on the [[World Wide Web]].

