'''ISTE''' is a science-technology [[publisher]], with publications on [[engineering]], [[information and communication technology]], [[materials science]], [[digital signal]] and [[image processing]], [[networks]]{{dn|date=January 2014}} and numerical methods.<ref>[http://www.iste.co.uk/index.php?a=i&ACTION=Static&Page=aboutiste ISTE-Official Website]</ref>
